      "description": "This vehicle is in truly mint, showroom-quality condition and has been meticulously preserved. The exterior paint is flawless with a deep, mirror-like shine and no imperfections, while the interior remains in pristine state, still smelling fresh with no signs of wear on the leather or upholstery. Mechanically, the car performs exactly as it did the day it left the factory, with all systems functioning perfectly and a comprehensive service history included. A buyer can expect a vehicle that requires zero immediate investment and represents the finest example of this model available on the market today.",
