    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a driver-focused example featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six, renowned for its individual throttle bodies and double VANOS variable valve timing. Power is managed via a tactile Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox and a factory M-variable limited-slip differential. This chassis has undergone essential preventative maintenance, including rear subframe reinforcement and a rod bearing service, ensuring structural and internal engine integrity. The suspension geometry remains tight with refreshed bushings, preserving the communicative steering rack and 50/50 weight distribution. While the exterior shows minor road-going patina, the mechanical vitals are synchronized for peak performance, offering a visceral 8,000 RPM redline experience.",
      "price": 34500.0,
